{"tid":554891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂潮牌將港台澳列國家 深夜IG急耍冧","createTime":"2018-02-09T02:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T02:57:56.000Z","uid":90739,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dbafd0b87a76540c86535814029f63eb5854013a","tid":554891,"uid":90739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/104533_a966f8cdd00a3ce0bd3f0bc44bef9c90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F104533_a966f8cdd00a3ce0bd3f0bc44bef9c90.png&h=9da1c9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余文樂就事件道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/104534_1aae3bc8b2c6fba9303096ee8749af20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F104534_1aae3bc8b2c6fba9303096ee8749af20.png&h=e24c9d11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/104535_4d76c5b85efb2f1482de2067549f5b51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F104535_4d76c5b85efb2f1482de2067549f5b51.png&h=cdeeb1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNBA名人堂球星余文樂4年前創立潮牌MADNESS，以簡約的藝術風格為號召，但由於官網寄送說明把台灣、香港及澳門都劃分成國家，令中國網民玻璃心盡碎，更揚言抵制。余文樂昨晚連忙撲火發道歉微博，官方IG也認錯說：「官方網站出現嚴重的表述錯誤，已第一時間進行修正」，擔心丟掉中國巿場。<br />\n<br />\nMADNESS官網上寫着「我們發送貨品到世界各地大部分國家，包括澳大利亞（澳洲）&hellip;&hellip;香港&hellip;&hellip;澳門&hellip;&hellip;台灣」，中國網友馬上把余文樂貼上「港獨」標籤，官方IG發現代誌大條後道歉說「今後將更加嚴格嚴謹審核」。<br />\n<br />\n余文樂昨晚在微博寫道：「我作為MADNESS的主理人，對於公司品牌監管不力，出現這麼大的錯誤和誤會，我難辭其咎，也感到非常抱歉。對於此事，我們將深刻檢討，日後工作中絕不容許此類錯誤再次發生！再次向所有關心我的人致歉！」對他潮牌生意有多少影響，還待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"7456f93d083657da6c2bab6510603f99ceda2bdc","tid":554891,"uid":13178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"冇撚用"},{"pid":"22a190d376f300a6e32f8507d07673892b5fbffe","tid":554891,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"想賺人仔就係咁架啦,鬼叫D人咁玻璃心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765c2209049f7610e5fb450c236aa9591efa0f30","tid":554891,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"文綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c326edbb22b6f5aaee1828dc8ee760e586eafc","tid":554891,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"支持樂囝"}]}